paragraphs.text:
%sql 
select 
    clean(fulltitle) title, 
    clean(description) desc, 
    clean(script.en[0].text) en, 
    clean(script.ko[0].text) kr, 
    'TBD' imagetag, 
    'TBD' ocr
from video 
where fulltitle like "%${Keyword}%" 
   or tags like '%${Keyword}%'
   or script.en like '%${Keyword}%'
   or script.ko like '%${Keyword}%' 
limit 5
